To write a ChatGPT prompt that takes a resume as input and parses the content in JSON format, you can define a clear structure for how you want the JSON output to look. Below is an example prompt and a Python script using OpenAI's API to achieve this:
Prompt

plaintext

You are an AI model that extracts structured information from resumes. Given a resume, parse its content into the following JSON format:

```json
{
  "name": "",
  "contact": {
    "email": "",
    "phone": "",
    "linkedin": "",
    "github": ""
  },
  "education": [
    {
      "degree": "",
      "field_of_study": "",
      "university": "",
      "location": "",
      "start_date": "",
      "end_date": "",
      "cgpa": ""
    }
  ],
  "experience": [
    {
      "position": "",
      "company": "",
      "location": "",
      "start_date": "",
      "end_date": "",
      "responsibilities": [""]
    }
  ],
  "projects": [
    {
      "title": "",
      "description": "",
      "technologies": [""],
      "link": ""
    }
  ],
  "certifications": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "issuer": "",
      "date": "",
      "credential_id": ""
    }
  ],
  "skills": [""]
}
